productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Allean has one of these. She works as a sky diver and she says it looks weedy.
The box this comes in is 5 foot by 6 inch and weights 17 pound!!!
heard about this on instrumental country radio, decided to give it a try.
My hummingbird loves to play with it.
This Berkshire works extremely well. It wetly improves my tennis by a lot.
